title: fanoutqa: What are the years of birth of the authors of the top 5 best-selling books? (00065f204bddb94d)

chat_history.content: What are the years of birth of the authors of the top 5 best-selling books?

Not all the authors of the top five best-selling books are known, but here are the birth years of the known authors:

* *The Little Prince* by Antoine de Saint-Exupéry, born in 1900
* *The Lord of the Rings* by J.R.R. Tolkien, born in 1892
* *The Hobbit* by J.R.R. Tolkien, born in 1892
